[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "そうだ！　ねえ、新曲聞いてみない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01065",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "そうね。どういう形になるにせよ、\n次のライブで披露するんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01066",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ほら、あんたも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01067",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "う、うむ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01068",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "楽しくていい曲だね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01069",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "年末のライブに向けた曲だけあって、\n賑やかな曲調でござるな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01070",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ふふん、さすが社長。なかなかいい仕事するじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01071",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "戻りましたわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01072",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "あ、社長！\nいきなり出て行くからびっくりしちゃったよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01073",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "いったいなんの用だったの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01074",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "改めて話をしてきましたわ。フェスの運営責任者と、\nそしてランターナ学園の理事長にも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01075",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "学園の……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01076",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "現在は長期休暇中……特に年末年始は部活動なども\nすべて休み。この学園は無人の「箱」となります",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01077",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "まさか……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01078",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ここ、ランターナ学園を\nカウントダウンフェスの会場とします！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01079",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "おおおおおおっ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01080",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "学園の校庭を臨時のライブ会場に改装し、\nそこに観客を入れる計画で各所進行中ですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01081",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "いや、確かに広さは十分だけど……\nいきなりそんなことできるの！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01082",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "もちろん、課題は山積みですわ。会場の設営以外にも、\nフードやドリンクの手配、近隣住民との交渉など……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01083",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "元々のスタッフだけでは手が足りませんから、\n臨時アルバイトを雇う予定ではありますが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01084",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "学園の生徒からも、「課外活動」という名目で\n協力者を募ってもよい、と許可を得ています",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01085",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "じゃあ、レスナちゃんたちにも声かけてみようよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01086",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "それならば錬金術の力も借りられないだろうか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01087",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "キューンたちにも手伝ってもらいましょ。\n同じ参加者なんだし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01088",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ、やる気ですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01089",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "本番に向けてのレッスンもありますが、\n可能な範囲で、それぞれできることをやりましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01090",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "三人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01091",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01092",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01093",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]